<h2>Option 1: File Online (Money Claim Online — MCOL)</h2>

<h3>Advantages of MCOL:</h3>
<ul>
  <li>✅ <strong>Lower court fee:</strong> £25 cheaper than paper filing for most claims</li>
  <li>✅ <strong>Faster processing:</strong> Issued within 24 hours</li>
  <li>✅ <strong>Track your claim online:</strong> Real-time updates</li>
  <li>✅ <strong>Request judgment and enforcement online:</strong> No need to send forms by post</li>
